  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要梳理一下物流系统的核心模块。首先是配送路线管理，我把它叫做Logistics_DeliveryRoute，这是整个流程的起点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Logistics_DeliveryRoute"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，DeliveryRoute是源头。那它和下游模块的关系是？比如它直接驱动库存还是通过其他环节？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "配送路线确定后，会直接影响库存分配。所以Audit要连到Define，Define也是Logistics_StockLevel，但代表库存决策节点。另外车队管理Logistics_FleetManagement也很重要，我记为Bail。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail",
        "Logistics_FleetManagement",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把Audit→Define和Bail节点加上。继续补充？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Audit",
        "Define",
        "Bail"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "车队和库存之间是双向的——Bail要指向Barg，同时Barg也返回Bail，这是调度循环。Barg就是Logistics_StockLevel的监控端。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Bail",
        "Barg",
        "Logistics_StockLevel"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "双向箭头，Bail↔Barg，理解。那仓库Code呢？Logistics_Warehouse放在什么位置？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Logistics_Warehouse"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "仓库是底层支撑，Code指向Define，表示实际库存反馈给决策层。另外我注意到还需要一个风险模块Risk，它通过Signal影响Barg。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加Code→Define和Risk→Signal→Barg的链条。Place和Press这对关系需要处理吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Code",
        "Define",
        "Risk",
        "Signal",
        "Barg",
        "Place",
        "Press"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "Place→Press是独立的压力触发机制，暂时不和其他主模块直接关联，保持并行。还有，Define本身也要直接连到Barg，表示决策到执行的落地。",
      "elements_involved": [
