        "Barg"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Define→Barg已补充。现在检查整体：Audit出发，分两支到Define和Bail；Bail与Barg循环；Code支撑Define；Risk通过Signal影响Barg；Place独立触发Press。结构对吗？",
